originalSql:
WITH RankedTitles AS (
    SELECT 
        title.id AS title_id,
        title.title AS title,
        title.production_year,
        title.kind_id,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY title.production_year ORDER BY title.title ASC) AS title_rank
    FROM 
        title
    WHERE 
        title.production_year IS NOT NULL
),
CastDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        cast_info.movie_id,
        COUNT(DISTINCT cast_info.person_id) AS actor_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT aka_name.name, ', ') AS actor_names
    FROM 
        cast_info
    JOIN 
        aka_name
    ON 
        cast_info.person_id = aka_name.person_id
    GROUP BY 
        cast_info.movie_id
),
MovieKeywords AS (
    SELECT 
        movie_keyword.movie_id,
        STRING_AGG(keyword.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
    FROM 
        movie_keyword
    JOIN 
        keyword
    ON 
        movie_keyword.keyword_id = keyword.id
    GROUP BY 
        movie_keyword.movie_id
),
MoviesWithDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        RankedTitles.title_id,
        RankedTitles.title,
        RankedTitles.production_year,
        CAST(COALESCE(CastDetails.actor_count, 0) AS INTEGER) AS actor_count,
        COALESCE(CastDetails.actor_names, 'None') AS actor_names,
        COALESCE(MovieKeywords.keywords, 'None') AS keywords
    FROM 
        RankedTitles
    LEFT JOIN 
        CastDetails
    ON 
        RankedTitles.title_id = CastDetails.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        MovieKeywords
    ON 
        RankedTitles.title_id = MovieKeywords.movie_id
)
SELECT 
    title_id,
    title,
    production_year,
    actor_count,
    actor_names,
    keywords
FROM 
    MoviesWithDetails
WHERE 
    production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2023
ORDER BY 
    production_year DESC, 
    title ASC

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "keyword", "phonetic_code"
FROM "keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("t7"."TITLE_ID", "t7"."TITLE_ID") AS "TITLE_ID", "t7"."TITLE", "t7"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t7"."ACTOR_COUNT", "t7"."ACTOR_NAMES", "t7"."KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."TITLE_ID", "t1"."TITLE", "t1"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", CAST(CASE WHEN "t3"."ACTOR_COUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."ACTOR_COUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS INTEGER) AS "ACTOR_COUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."ACTOR_NAMES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."ACTOR_NAMES" AS VARCHAR) ELSE 'None' END AS "ACTOR_NAMES", CASE WHEN "t5"."KEYWORDS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t5"."KEYWORDS" AS VARCHAR) ELSE 'None' END AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM (SELECT "id" AS "TITLE_ID", "title" AS "TITLE", "production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "kind_id" AS "KIND_ID", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "production_year" ORDER BY "title") AS "TITLE_RANK"
FROM "title") AS "t0"
WHERE "PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000 AND "PRODUCTION_YEAR" <= 2023) AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "cast_info"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."person_id") AS "ACTOR_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTOR_NAMES"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
GROUP BY "cast_info"."movie_id") AS "t3" ON "t1"."TITLE_ID" = "t3"."MOVIE_ID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", LISTAGG("s1"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "s1"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "s1"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
GROUP BY "movie_keyword"."movie_id") AS "t5" ON "t1"."TITLE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
ORDER BY "t1"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t1"."TITLE") AS "t7"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "movie_id", "keyword_id"
FROM "movie_keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("t7"."TITLE_ID", "t7"."TITLE_ID") AS "TITLE_ID", "t7"."TITLE", "t7"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t7"."ACTOR_COUNT", "t7"."ACTOR_NAMES", "t7"."KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."TITLE_ID", "t1"."TITLE", "t1"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", CAST(CASE WHEN "t3"."ACTOR_COUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."ACTOR_COUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS INTEGER) AS "ACTOR_COUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."ACTOR_NAMES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."ACTOR_NAMES" AS VARCHAR) ELSE 'None' END AS "ACTOR_NAMES", CASE WHEN "t5"."KEYWORDS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t5"."KEYWORDS" AS VARCHAR) ELSE 'None' END AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM (SELECT "id" AS "TITLE_ID", "title" AS "TITLE", "production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "kind_id" AS "KIND_ID", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "production_year" ORDER BY "title") AS "TITLE_RANK"
FROM "title") AS "t0"
WHERE "PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000 AND "PRODUCTION_YEAR" <= 2023) AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "cast_info"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."person_id") AS "ACTOR_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTOR_NAMES"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
GROUP BY "cast_info"."movie_id") AS "t3" ON "t1"."TITLE_ID" = "t3"."MOVIE_ID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "s1"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", LISTAGG("keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "keyword"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "keyword"."id" = "s1"."keyword_id"
GROUP BY "s1"."movie_id") AS "t5" ON "t1"."TITLE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
ORDER BY "t1"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t1"."TITLE") AS "t7"
